Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.75,0:00:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.63,0:00:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.20,0:00:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.02,0:00:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.34,0:00:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.59,0:00:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:01:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yugi's Desperate Battle:\N Orgoth's Violent Attack"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go, Otogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-O-V-E, Otogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.77,0:01:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go, Otogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.52,0:01:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat that treacherous Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.90,0:01:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised us you wouldn't talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.44,0:01:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me say this one thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare call Yugi's soul battle in the Duelist Kingdom {\i1}treacherous{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, {\i1}Pegasus{\i0} was the treacherous one, using his Mind Scan and all that crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing you say to Otogi-kun will get through now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:02:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Otogi-kun strongly believes Yugi ruined his dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what {\i1}can{\i0} we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has to feel Yugi's {\i1}soul{\i0} through the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! This battle ain't just about me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, this is a battle to protect your manhood!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lo-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ser-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dog!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lo... ser... {\i1}dog{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right. I'm a loser dog alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Loser dog~! Loser dog~! Loser dog~!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, Jounouchi lost whatever shred of dignity he had left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Loser dog" sure hits the nail on the head, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sounds {\i1}just{\i0} like a loser dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How do I make Otogi understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's got to be a hint in this game!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dice Roll!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can I make Otogi understand the heart of the game he made himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's only one way to reach Otogi's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gathered what I need to activate an Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using two Magic Crests, Gorogon moves forward in a straight line,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,destroying both enemy and ally Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use two Magic Crests!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rolling Crush!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate its Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use three more Magic Crests and use the Rolling Crush once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No~!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bow wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with all the commotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it coming from the new game store?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Who the hell's doing that?! Stop touching me! \N-Sorry, youngsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.15,0:04:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go, Otogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it! You can do it, Otogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so good my heart almost stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you in the enemy's Duel Ring?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet down, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're trying to watch here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're blocking the screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monsters can only attack once per turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But a Monster's Special Ability is a special exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, the fact that you actually discovered that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were nothing but a shy nerd at first, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frankly, I thought this game was nothing but nonsense when I first heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dungeon Dice Monsters is really fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can sure see why you wanted to spread this game over the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really think you can get out of this by {\i1}praising{\i0} me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A match is a match!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and the game is only getting started!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dice Roll!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So my Summon failed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dice Roll!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A successful Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dimension Dice!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duker of Twin Swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't launch an attack on any of your Monsters yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll store my Movement Crest in my Pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be finally getting used to the game, Yugi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? I don't really get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}still{\i0} don't get the rules of this game?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to use the Crests you rolled when you Summon a Monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can store them away in the Crest Pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! So that's what you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, you're slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you challenged Otogi-kun in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we called you a loser dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's seriously hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:07:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's started to learn this game at an amazing speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got to completely crush you before you learn all the rules of the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}my{\i0} turn!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dice Roll!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a pair of Summon Crests!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dimension Dice!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon the Level 2 Minotaur!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use four of my stored Movement Crests to move Minotaur into position!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minotaur!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack the Duker of Twin Swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It gets stronger when fighting against Warrior-types!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Attack Power rises from 10 to 30 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use Duker of Twin Swords' Defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:07:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got 10 Defense Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duker of Twin Swords has 10 Defense Points, and took damage of 30!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it now has 10 Hit Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's completely mastered Defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dice Roll!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the cost for its Special Attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use two Attack Crests!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twin Sword Multiple Slashes!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My... Minotaur got...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No~!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otogi-kun~!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just started playing, too! That's our Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otogi, it seems we've come right back to the start line!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I admit it was really magnificent for you to be able to beat my Minotaur!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're hugely mistaken if you think some newbie
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can completely master Dungeon Dice Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This game isn't decided just by Monster battles!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still haven't noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a close look at the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh {\i1}no{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, {\i1}no{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Yugi discover something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll have to explain it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You use the dice to Summon a Monster, as well as expand the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're meant to connect it to your own Dungeon corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before when Otogi-kun kept dimensioning the dice, he completely locked Yugi into a corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning Yugi already...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:11:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means Yugi stands no hope of winning against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there any other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he just has to find out how to Summon his Monster in the enemy's Dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy's Dungeon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to do that, he'd have to defeat my entire Monster army,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and get himself within striking distance of me, the Dungeon Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible, even for Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A black... die?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is known as the "Rare Black"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look at what happens when you roll the black die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dice Roll!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Summon's a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dimension, Rare Black!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon the Level 3 Warp Hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Warp Item!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Warp?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can warp a special Item,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and one of those things...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the true power of the Warp Item...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is the dimension the Rare Black places on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an entrance...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a warp leading directly to another location, becoming an exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still one place left on my field where I can play the Dimension Dice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When two Warp Holes are on the field, his Monsters can teleport between them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you {\i1}finally{\i0} realized?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I get my other Rare Black,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can teleport my Monster army to your side of the field in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:13:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using this Rare Black combo,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my victory is assured!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Warp Hole...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I can do is strengthen my defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dice Roll!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Summon's a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dimension Dice!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon the Level 3 Swift Black Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Ninja has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Ninja...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But can he beat the speed of my Rare Black Combo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here! The black die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I Dimension it, the Rare Black Combo will be complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go! Otogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dice Roll!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not good...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:14:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If he completes the Rare Black Combo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life is spared for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otogi, it seems you've overlooked something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have one as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Rare Black!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Yugi!\N -Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dice Roll!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A successful Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dimension, Rare Black Die!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then use Swift Black Ninja's Instant Movement!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swift Black Ninja, attack the Gargoyle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assassination complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got him~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because Otogi's Dungeon covers the entire field,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}my Dungeon space connects to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Using the Warp Hole to get past his battle line is the only way to prevail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Before he Summons the Warp Crest,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to stop his Warp Hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Ninja is an especially tricky Monster due to its Instant Movement ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He moves three spaces when you use a Movement Crest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi's bound to attack me next turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't Summon a defense Monster this turn, I'm screwed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A failed Summon...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dice Roll!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Movement Crest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Black Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Ninja, attack Dungeon Master Otogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall take your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No~!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cruel~!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bow wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now this is in the bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my grandson for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:16:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it, old fart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To harm {\i1}me{\i0} in Dungeon Dice Monsters...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I expected of the Duelist Kingdom victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're making me really excited, Yugi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be touching me again!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got some Summon Crests!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dimension Dice!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon the Level 3 God Orgoth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Orgoth's Special Ability allows me to take three Magic Crests
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.92,0:17:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and raise its Attack from 10 to 20!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use a Movement Crest on God Orgoth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Orgoth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack the Swift Black Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diamond Blade!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't do something, I'm done...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look at the Dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment God Orgoth attacked,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used a Trap Crest to activate his Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swift Black Ninja has the Effect to dodge any attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Invisibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It camouflaged itself like a chameleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was able to avoid the attack that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's no longer like the person who could hardly play D.D.M...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:18:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi Mutou...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it possible he beat Pegasus without tricks, but with pure talent?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swift Black Ninja, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No~!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great job!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one more attack and I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't let you do as you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a fight for me to get my broken dream back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Orgoth, attack the Swift Black Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't have any more Trap Crests in my Crest Pool...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I no longer have a way to stop his attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diamond Blade!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My only Monster in enemy territory was beaten...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My opponent has four Monsters at his disposal...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I only have three Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(147,136)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the Warp Hole, Yugi's Dungeon is invaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Orgoth has begun to eliminate all of Yugi's Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he doesn't Summon a Monster soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he'll lose all of his Life Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't even have a space to Summon a Monster in anymore...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.72,0:20:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Miracle Dimension:\N Summon the Black Magician"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.34,0:21:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The flask shines bright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}waiting in the Science Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By rubbing our cold hands together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They will become warm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.92,0:21:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll shower all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will support your lonely back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.76,0:21:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.42,0:22:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you're surrounded by a ring of friendship
